title: Classic_MP6410_Driver_Disk.iso
description:
Original driver disk for Classic MP6410 MP3 player.

I just found the install CD to my old Classic MP6410 MP3 player. I have been looking for the drivers on the internet for a while with no luck. I did discover that there are quite a few other people out there that were looking for these drivers as well. So... Here is the second torrent I have ever created:

A near impossible to find driver disk for an obsolete piece of hardware!!!

Enjoy!
